==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mechanist
<hw>Mech"an*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A maker of
machines; one skilled in mechanics.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who regards the phenomena of nature as the
effects of forces merely mechanical.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>mechanization</ent>⟦br⟧
